metadata.description:
LNRZ SZN 2 WK 2

Eldar Zey has produced with artists like Daniel Allan, DLG., Deegan, Reo Cragun, Pluko, and many more, but has never released under his own name.

Until now.

Amber is a sonic exploration and a true feat of sound design & imagination. The first of many Eldar Zey releases.

A quote from LNRZ team member DLG. :

"Eldar is a mad scientist of music and it makes me so happy he's releasing his own songs finally that I might cry"

Join LNRZ HQ here: https://guild.xyz/lnrz-hq
